1. Nationality:nigerian == Color:turquise
2. Nationality:swedish == Pet:hamster
3. Nationality:japanese == Beverage:soy-milk
4. Color:brown is on the left of Color:lavender
5. Color:brown == Beverage:lemonade
6. Cigar:davidoff == Pet:goat
7. Color:emerald == Cigar:old-henry
8. Beverage:almond-milk is in the middle
9. Nationality:indonesian is on the far left
10. Cigar:cain is on the left or right of Pet:ferret
11. Pet:rats is on the left or right of Cigar:old-henry
12. Cigar:pinkmaster == Beverage:mirinda
13. Nationality:indian == Cigar:aristoff
14. Nationality:indonesian is on the left or right of Color:pink
15. Cigar:cain is on the left or right of Beverage:hot-chocolate

